c)
CRC Cards for 5 Classes

CRC = Class – Responsibilities – Collaborators

1. CRC Card – Customer
| Class            | Customer                                                                                    |
| ---------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Responsibilities | Register with system, Manage subscription, Request weekly schedule, View bill, Make payment |
| Collaborators    | Subscription, Bill, Payment                                                                 |

2. CRC Card – Subscription
| Class            | Subscription                                                                     |
| ---------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Responsibilities | Store subscribed channels, Add channels, Remove channels, Store schedule request |
| Collaborators    | Customer, Channel                                                                |

3. CRC Card – Channel
| Class            | Channel                                        |
| ---------------- | ---------------------------------------------- |
| Responsibilities | Maintain channel details, Provide TV schedules |
| Collaborators    | Subscription, TVSchedule                       |

4. CRC Card – Bill
| Class            | Bill                                                                         |
| ---------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Responsibilities | Generate monthly bill, Calculate subscription charges, Send bill to customer |
| Collaborators    | Customer, Subscription, Payment                                              |

5. CRC Card – Payment
| Class            | Payment                                            |
| ---------------- | -------------------------------------------------- |
| Responsibilities | Process credit card payment, Store payment details |
| Collaborators    | Customer, Bill                                     |

